## üîß **PL/SQL Components**

### **Core Functions**
1. **`fn_AnalyzeZoneHealth(zon)`** - Returns water quality status
2. **`fn_CalculateWaterNeed(zon)`** - Computes irrigation requirements
3. **`fn_CheckSensorHealth(zon)`** - Validates sensor data quality

### **Stored Procedures**
1. **`usp_GenerateWateringSchedule`** - Daily task generation
2. **`usp_ProcessSensorReadings`** - Bulk data processing
3. **`usp_ResolveAlert`** - Alert management workflow

### **Triggers**
1. **`trg_CriticalAlert`** - Automatic alert on threshold breach
2. **`trg_AuditChanges`** - Track all DML operations
3. **`trg_ValidateSensorData`** - Data quality assurance

### **Packages**
1. **`IRRIGATION_PKG`** - Main business logic package
2. **`REPORTING_PKG`** - Analytics and reporting functions

